# Dependency upgrades

After bumping `nuxt`, `@nuxtjs/supabase`, `@google/genai`, or `supabase` CLI:

1. Re-read module docs for **env var** and **breaking** changes.
2. Run `npm run build` and `nuxt prepare`.
3. Verify admin login and intake invite cookie still work.
4. Confirm Gemini model names still valid (`GEMINI_MODELS` in `server/utils/geminiShared.ts`).
5. Smoke-test parse: text PDF + image/Canva PDF (`scripts/test-pdf-vision.mjs`).

Pin major upgrades in dedicated PRs; do not mix with feature work.
